  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the onion, ginger, and garlic and cook, stirring occasionally, until the onion is translucent, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the berbere spice mix and cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Add the chickpeas and cook for 2 minutes, stirring occasionally.",
    "Add the chopped kale and cook until wilted, about 2 minutes.",
    "Crumble the taleggio cheese into the skillet and stir until melted and combined with the kale mixture.",
    "Season with salt and black pepper to taste.",
    "Transfer the mixture to a bamboo tray or serving dish.",
    "Drizzle with lemon juice and serve immediately."
  ],
